.TH "RTCINBOUNDRTPSTREAMSTATS.FRAMESRECEIVED" "3JS" "August 15, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.framesReceived \- RTCInboundRtpStreamStats:
framesReceived property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]framesReceived\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCInboundRtpStreamStats\f[R] dictionary indicates the total
number of complete frames received on this RTP stream over its lifetime.
.PP
Note that this may be lower than the total number of media source
frames, which is provided in \f[CR]RTCVideoSourceStats.frames\f[R].
.RS
.PP
\f[B]Note:\f[R] The value is undefined for audio streams.
.RE
.SH VALUE
A positive number.
